1. Satori
   License: Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL-2.0)
   Copyright (c) Vercel
   Source: https://github.com/vercel/satori
   
   This package is a modified version of Vercel's Satori library.
   Modifications include:
   - Added JSDOM support for HTML/CSS parsing
   - Added built-in font loading utilities
   - Added font management system
   
   The original Satori library and all modifications are licensed under MPL-2.0.

